Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要的东西马上丢掉 这是我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以养成了整理物品的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能留在手里的东西终归有限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总要轻装上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件雨衣… 是和友香一起去买的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香 你正在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs70\pos(922,114)\bord4\shad2\4c&HFFFFDD&\3c&HCABD76&\c&HF7F4F3&}雨衣的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(876,184)\bord4\shad2\4c&HFFFFDD&\3c&HCABD76&\c&HF7F4F3&}～友香 你正在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身材好 人也聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是个怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还爬山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人不怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 初中时我给人的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 又受伤了？ 在山里？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 稍微擦破皮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子一个人去爬山不危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 友香 替我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是一个人爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都自由自在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你又要去爬高山了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装备够吗？ 真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次给你带特产回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别着急啦 不会给你添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有那么危险么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没给友香添麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 心里似乎还有一种别样的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 心里好不痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又受这么重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微扭了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪是稍微扭了一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么没事啊 这还算没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是被讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不至于那么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没给她添麻烦…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算我这么想 友香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算装出笑脸向她道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没认真听过她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是横冲直撞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顾周围往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香担心我 我也觉得不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 友香并不是表面应和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是打心里担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却没认真对待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这人真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人一起走的时候 要照顾对方的步子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人交往也是一个道理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走得太快 拉开太远 就该停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着对方追上自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那么替我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会注意安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这些 是不是晚了点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也说得太过了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时没忍住…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所缺少的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总也整理不顺的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕谁都不肯搭理自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香听我说 我以前都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有人担心 有人生气 是多么幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想买件新雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在穿的已经破了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能跟你一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 稍微有些兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 机会难得 想让你再穿出点女人味来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是不是太女性化了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样正好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫你身材又好 个子又高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 多可惜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下来去买雨衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢 种类好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山的时候雨衣很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么夸张？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光防雨 还能防风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 更多时候用来防寒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在山上 雨水会从四面八方袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨伞不管用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说好贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了登山加上各种功能就贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好轻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 又轻又结实又防水 还能透汗呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集成了这么多功能的料子 自然就贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他还有防水手套 防雨裙之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这种冲锋裤 穿着鞋都能穿进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前啊 登山的时候下雨了都要命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我好像明白你其实也在照顾自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 打算买哪件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件看着不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颜色和你很搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就它了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 还是这件的颜色…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑 开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我逛这么久 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太见外了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是都说了 对你在做的事情感兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你啊 时不时缺根筋的 让人不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 遇到危险就给你打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你来救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的不是这个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气的表情不可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件冲锋衣 尺寸不合适 已经穿不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎么舍得丢掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说友香 现在在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 友香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没干？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那陪我去买东西好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去所泽 看看登山装备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少请你吃蛋糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那30分后 在车站前面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮件？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐好 我想去爬谷川岳 想请教学姐一下（>人<）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发送！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川岳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前友香担心我 这次大概轮到我去担心小葵了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经孤独地走着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在已经不再孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身边有友香和小葵她们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 友香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又穿成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不穿出女人味来 多可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前就跟你说很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 UFO！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你！别蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气的表情不可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不站住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,並んで歩いてたら自然に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,二人三脚なってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:23.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,透明リボンで結ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:27.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ひとりで描く夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:32.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ふたりなら立体的になる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:35.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,キュンときて上昇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:39.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,スタッカートみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:43.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,胸を叩くワクワク感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:47.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,それに つきあってくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:51.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,気の合う Dear My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,地球色パレット
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,混ぜて明日は何色?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,不思議 不安より
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:09.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しみの容量が増えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,また明日！ヤッホー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}肩并肩走着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}自然就会挽起双手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:23.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}透明的蝴蝶结 系紧两人的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:27.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一个人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:32.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}两人一起就会变得立体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:35.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}跟着心跳上升！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:43.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}昂扬感像断奏音符般拍打胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:51.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}身边还有陪伴我的知心 Dear My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}地球湛蓝调色板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}调出明天未知的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}真奇妙 不但没有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:09.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}快乐的容量反而更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}明天再见！YAHOO
